description: Apply when editing OpenAPI to keep schema-first & non-breaking changes
globs: ["api/openapi.yaml"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Edit schema first; generate stubs/clients from it.
- Provide examples for 2xx/4xx/5xx; document types/nullability.
- Avoid breaking changes; if unavoidable, mark MAJOR bump and write migration notes.
